OL,3,CMan denies murder of 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Ckilled while helping woman
OL,6,FA man has denied the murder of a "good
OL,7,FSamaritan" who died after being hit by
OL,8,Fa car while trying to help a stranger.
OL,10,FHassan Jhangur, 23, also pleaded not
OL,11,Fguilty to Chris Marriott's
OL,12,Fmanslaughter, but admitted causing his
OL,13,Fdeath by dangerous driving when he
OL,14,Fappeared at Sheffield Crown Court on
OL,15,FFriday.
