OL,3,CMan denies murder of 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Ckilled while helping woman
OL,6,FFather-of-two Mr Marriott, 46, died
OL,7,Fafter he went to the aid of a woman he
OL,8,Fsaw unconscious in the street during a
OL,9,Fdisturbance in the Burngreave area of
OL,10,FSheffield last December, police have
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FAs he tended to the woman on College
OL,14,FClose on 27 December, a car hit the
OL,15,Fcrowd, leaving a number of people
OL,16,Finjured.
OL,18,FMr Marriott, who had been out for a
OL,19,Fwalk with his wife and two sons, died
OL,20,Ffrom his injuries. Police later
OL,21,Fdescribed him as a "good Samaritan".
