OL,3,CMan denies murder of 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Ckilled while helping woman
OL,6,FMr Jhangur, of Whiteways Road,
OL,7,FSheffield, admitted causing serious
OL,8,Finjury to four other people by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving. They are Alison
OL,10,FNorris, Ambreen Jhangur, Nafeesa
OL,11,FJhangur and Riasat Khan.
OL,13,FMs Norris is a midwife who also went
OL,14,Fto help at the scene.
OL,16,FMr Jhangur also denied attempting to
OL,17,Fmurder Hasan Khan and wounding him
OL,18,Fwith intent.
