OL,3,CMan denies murder of 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Ckilled while helping woman
OL,6,FThe defendant pleaded not guilty to
OL,7,Fthree charges of causing grievous
OL,8,Fbodily harm with intent, in relation
OL,9,Fto Ms Norris, Ambreen Jhangur and
OL,10,FNafeesa Jhangur.
OL,12,FAnd he denied one count of wounding
OL,13,Fwith intent, in relation to Riasat
OL,14,FKhan.
OL,16,FThe defendant sat in the dock with his
OL,17,Ffather Mohammed Jhangur, 56, of
OL,18,FWhiteways Road, Sheffield, who denied
OL,19,Fattempting to pervert the course of
OL,20,Fpublic justice. The charge relates to
OL,21,Fhim allegedly concealing a knife.
