OL,3,CMan denies murder of 'good Samaritan'
OL,4,Ckilled while helping woman
OL,6,FBoth men will go on trial on 17 June
OL,7,Fat Sheffield Crown Court, the judge
OL,8,FMrs Justice Lambert told the court.
OL,10,FMr Jhangur was remanded in custody.
OL,11,FMohammed Jhangur was released on
OL,12,Fconditional bail.
OL,14,FThe pair were told to appear for a pre-
OL,15,Ftrial review hearing on 3 June.
